query:
UPDATE users 
        SET height_cm = COALESCE($1, height_cm),
            current_weight_kg = COALESCE($2, current_weight_kg),
            gender = COALESCE($3, gender),
            date_of_birth = COALESCE($4, date_of_birth),
            activity_level = COALESCE($5, activity_level)
        WHERE id = $6
